To get into what they mean for Americans from Main Street to Wall Street, What’s News brings you an episode of our sister podcast WSJ’s Take On the Week, where co-hosts Telis Demos and Miriam Gottfried discuss tariffs, Trump’s trade war and the upcoming first quarter earnings season.
